rmal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好到極啲豬手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9a14c31ac30b99ab364ca1ec620a82dabd6ebb","tid":385574,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:56:48.000Z","msg":"大角咀昌興麵家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0d70019410c5fe2ab3750115c540909db89f4f","tid":385574,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩係細蓉牙死蝗蟲</blockquote><br />\n你黎搞笑架 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7b68765ddc1ff3c83cd240977005fbb6bee989","tid":385574,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雲吞麵就雲吞麵啦</blockquote><br />\non9仔 分清楚先好上支連登講野啦 唔撚同架屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你解釋下有咩分別呀不如?"},{"pid":"1d4e8ca1462bc99baed141abd4033bed57ec9ab0","tid":385574,"uid":16528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雲吞麵就雲吞麵啦</blockquote><br />\non9仔 分清楚先好上支連登講野啦 唔撚同架屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你解釋下有咩分別呀不如?</blockquote><br />\n講啦柒頭<br />\n<br />\n雲吞麵同細蓉根本無分別<br />\n細蓉 中蓉 大蓉<br />\n講緊大細<br />\n細就係一兩麵四粒雲吞<br />\n大就兩倍<br />\n<br />\n叻唔切<br />\n柒少陣啦"},{"pid":"e357bb89ec0027261df564108ba2ed9009fe7251","tid":385574,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雲吞麵就雲吞麵啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 升中未啊？</blockquote><br />\n唔係雲吞麵另一種叫法？<br />\n只不過係一碗細嘅雲吞麵</blockquote><br />\n加陣度度食都係比細蓉既份量你啦<br />\n根本無分別<br />\n除非你想叫大蓉<br />\n<br />\n識條撚咩班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24ade1421d6227eceb083e56f546998081c9f62","tid":385574,"uid":5846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"細蓉係廣東地道叫法，以前的確仲有中蓉同大蓉。<br />\n<br />\n細蓉就好似碟頭飯之類嘅俗稱，講細蓉都要批鬥人同隻癲狗有乜分別"},{"pid":"fb846e03296c860e22b076287a131f316aac9445","tid":385574,"uid":97550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"麥奀始終最好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d059075071abf5ee2491b996352697d64872cce","tid":385574,"uid":141706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>九龍有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n麥文記</blockquote><br />\n細細個開始食,食左10年8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a159f19c2b9b47bd95d9b509af45dc5421d46589","tid":385574,"uid":135469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:15:26.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣沾仔記"},{"pid":"72da79316544eb0433817f210642e04406e6cffd","tid":385574,"uid":42680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打食過劉森記？可唔可以分享下"},{"pid":"edd98bc556cb3b96929742a8d9ef3af190755157","tid":385574,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打食過劉森記？可唔可以分享下</blockquote><br />\n食過，麻麻地"},{"pid":"da482d7f5421d752cd39e30bed9e7a4b2c752988","tid":385574,"uid":68109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:21:14.000Z","msg":"太子興記"},{"pid":"570b687165869daf218bd92d52f0ddf380bc6761","tid":385574,"uid":19627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太子興記</blockquote><br />\n剛剛追晒成個post都想講興記 咁啱巴打講 <br />\n不過天氣熱 佢呢度食就慘啲"},{"pid":"8452267fde0dc392f9994c42c1848ba53b44960c","tid":385574,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雲吞麵就雲吞麵啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 升中未啊？</blockquote><br />\n唔係雲吞麵另一種叫法？<br />\n只不過係一碗細嘅雲吞麵</blockquote><br />\n加陣度度食都係比細蓉既份量你啦<br />\n根本無分別<br />\n除非你想叫大蓉<br />\n<br />\n識條撚咩班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫細蓉就好似去餐廳食野用英文叫野食一樣<br />\n成個人好似高檔左"},{"pid":"171b22dea33711cd06f9670af5379232640b3d20","tid":385574,"uid":62830,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雲吞麵就雲吞麵啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 升中未啊？</blockquote><br />\n唔係雲吞麵另一種叫法？<br />\n只不過係一碗細嘅雲吞麵</blockquote><br />\n加陣度度食都係比細蓉既份量你啦<br />\n根本無分別<br />\n除非你想叫大蓉<br />\n<br />\n識條撚咩班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫細蓉就好似去餐廳食野用英文叫野食一樣<br />\n成個人好似高檔左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n古老當時興，我老豆老母都唔會講呢句野啦，民初時期咩，諗下都覺得柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果同朋友出去食野佢無啦啦叫一句細蓉真係尷尬死"},{"pid":"1ef16496c8fbbae38286b9ec9009f5097bc5e6ed","tid":385574,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打食過劉森記？可唔可以分享下</blockquote><br />\n食過，麻麻地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry上面我記錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿媽係話劉森記唔好食<br />\n唔係巴打推介果間"},{"pid":"90ac9b502e088d1c4dbb367a402ad4d5182e8fea","tid":385574,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雲吞麵就雲吞麵啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 升中未啊？</blockquote><br />\n唔係雲吞麵另一種叫法？<br />\n只不過係一碗細嘅雲吞麵</blockquote><br />\n加陣度度食都係比細蓉既份量你啦<br />\n根本無分別<br />\n除非你想叫大蓉<br />\n<br />\n識條撚咩班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫細蓉就好似去餐廳食野用英文叫野食一樣<br />\n成個人好似高檔左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n古老當時興，我老豆老母都唔會講呢句野啦，民初時期咩，諗下都覺得柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果同朋友出去食野佢無啦啦叫一句細蓉真係尷尬死</blockquote><br />\n收嗲啦垃圾"},{"pid":"79f3f4a621e96183a3d3f0c036b5a18cb97d38bf","tid":385574,"uid":52975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:55:25.000Z","msg":"其實麥文記最好食係薑葱撈麵加個淨雲吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9157a57d345fc1bd27767642f78687d9175d0adb","tid":385574,"uid":42680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打食過劉森記？可唔可以分享下</blockquote><br />\n食過，麻麻地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry上面我記錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿媽係話劉森記唔好食<br />\n唔係巴打推介果間</blockquote><br />\n謝謝平反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a822d43929ce6b1a1cce9023dd65904a1ffdfd33","tid":385574,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:23:01.000Z","msg":"興記長期無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77ff965d59b62d1e46ffd4b860d26f9b18c2c70","tid":385574,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:23:28.000Z","msg":"但真係唔錯<br />\n慢工出細貨"},{"pid":"ab00c716d3fe8fe308c6ab9f1d12bf4cdc137800","tid":385574,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"屌你細蓉都唔識果啲正一垃圾蝗蟲"},{"pid":"491f591bc1babe23c7ddaf8191c3fa4320e21f92","tid":385574,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打食過劉森記？可唔可以分享下</blockquote><br />\n食過，麻麻地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry上面我記錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿媽係話劉森記唔好食<br />\n唔係巴打推介果間</blockquote><br />\n謝謝平反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己就唔識分好唔好食（平時好少食）<br />\n所以直頭都唔太記得邊間打邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買畀阿媽食多<br />\n有機會去下坤記先  謝"}]}